30. I remember reading about how many different ways there were to enter Castle Greyhawk in Gary Gygax's home campaign and I liked that a lot. I wanted to have at least two separate entrances on the first level, possibly more, as well as entrances to deeper levels. I did follow through with this, but not to the extent I originally imagined.}
