I thought about it a bit more and I came up with the notion that kobolds could be created by corrupting the bodies of dead dwarves, restoring them to some twisted semblance of life. This wasn't a power kobolds possessed naturally, but something certain demons knew, which is why kobolds often serve demons (or their representatives). }{\i0\ai0\rtlch \ltrch\loch
I was pleased with this idea, because it provide me with a means to include a demon of some sort on Level 1, something I rarely saw in the other dungeons of my acquaintance.}
